race.description: Spry Civil Construction Stake Pr2 Division1
race.comment: FINNISS HONOUR (7) carved over from wide out and boxed on strongly to finish 1.3 lengths away in second (19.78) behind Ocean Fury at this track. Rates highly and will give a great sight. CARRY ON CASEY (5) struggled for best form latest, finishing 5th (22.84) in a Grade 6 at Murray Bridge. Has never missed the frame here at the trip including one win. Still to record a win from this draw but has never missed the frame in two starts. Should be about the money. VICTA GRAHAM (1) recorded his 3rd career win last time out (17.03) at this track and drawn box 1 for the first time here. Comes through a solid form race last start. One of main contenders. IZZY LETTS (8) has been in the placings at her last two runs, most recently when third (31.21) in a Grade 6 over 530m at Angle Park.
